ce that works 24/7 \u2014 capturing leads while you're on the job, not chasing them after.</p>\n\n      <!-- DIVIDER -->\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:36px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"border-top:1px solid #2A2A2A;\"></td></tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <!-- BUSINESS TAG -->\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;color:#888888;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;\">Built for</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;color:#F5F5F5;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.3px;\">Platinum Pool &amp; Property Services LLC</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 36px;color:#888888;font-size:13px;\">Pool &amp; Property Services &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; Inland Empire, CA</p>\n\n      <!-- PRIMARY CTA -->\n      <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"border:1px solid #C4A35A;border-radius:4px;\">\n            <a href=\"https://mona-chat-ap.onrender.com/platinum-pool\" style=\"display:block;padding:15px 36px;color:#C4A35A;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;\">See What We Built For You &nbsp;\u2192</a>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <!-- SECONDARY CTA -->\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 36px;color:#666666;font-size:13px;\">Or <a href=\"mailto:monaempoweryou@gmail.com\" style=\"color:#C4A35A;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;\">reply to this email</a> \u2014 we read every response.</p>\n\n      <!-- DIVIDER -->\n      <table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:32px;\">\n        <tr><td style=\"border-top:1px solid #2A2A2A;\"></td></tr>\n      </table>\n\n      <!-- CONFIDENCE STATEMENT -->\n      <p style=\"margin:0;color:#555555;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;font-style:italic;\">No obligation. No pressure. We built this because we believe your business deserves a